{"tid":2143659,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★公共醫療醫生協會憂自行咽喉採樣　可能弄斷誤吞拭子棒","createTime":"2020-08-07T08:21:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-25T15:34:49.000Z","uid":19454,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3c46ea622d112273acd1fbece6d4b11ae36f07b4","tid":2143659,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T08:21:01.000Z","msg":"公共醫療醫生協會表示，由市民自行採集咽喉樣本會產生幾個嚴重問題。她說，即使由醫護人員採集咽喉樣本，被檢查人士的咽喉都可能受傷，如果由市民自行採集，擔心經驗不足者，可能弄斷咽喉拭子棒，造成吞下異物的意外。<br />\n<br />\n協會列舉採集咽喉樣本的問題，包括可能因為不正確採集，減低檢測結果的準確性，結果比使用深喉唾液測試更「粗糙」及不可靠。對部分有長期病患，例如有血液凝固障礙、長期服食薄血丸或抗血小板藥物等人士，採集咽喉樣本時，如用力過度，有可能引致創傷及流血問題。採集咽喉樣本過程中，可能會引致咳嗽或打噴嚏等不適反應，產生飛沫亦可以傳播疾病。<br />\n<br />\n協會認為，由香港研發深喉唾液樣本及檢測方法，不會對接受檢測人士造成創傷，採集樣本技巧容易掌握，適合市民自行在家採集樣本使用，過程中亦不會出現霧化情況。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1542401-20200807.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1542401-20200807.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=ACvVw7CXGjn4pyDVYlJlLDmKloJy7KF%2B4xCSYNi8ivs%3D&h=b4bb51d6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1542401-20200807.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=6cfb056b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1542401-20200807.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"6fb9cd575b56337a56dde2641c128d5b80e03db1","tid":2143659,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T08:21:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b70508f64414bee1b9ed86412f7555b8320163f","tid":2143659,"uid":5178,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTim